## 9️⃣ 실전 예제

### 예제 1: 면적 계산

```rust
fn calculate_circle_area(radius: i32) -> f64 {
    let pi = 3.14159;
    pi * (radius as f64) * (radius as f64)
}

fn main() {
    let area = calculate_circle_area(5);
    println!("반지름 5의 원의 면적: {:.2}", area);
}
```

### 예제 2: 팩토리얼 (재귀)

```rust
fn factorial(n: i32) -> i32 {
    if n <= 1 {
        1
    } else {
        n * factorial(n - 1)
    }
}

fn main() {
    println!("5! = {}", factorial(5));  // 120
}
```

### 예제 3: 여러 함수 조합

```rust
fn is_even(n: i32) -> bool {
    n % 2 == 0
}

fn count_even(from: i32, to: i32) -> i32 {
    let mut count = 0;
    for i in from..=to {
        if is_even(i) {
            count += 1;
        }
    }
    count
}

fn main() {
    let result = count_even(1, 10);
    println!("1~10 중 짝수: {}개", result);  // 5개
}
```

